From 6fc626d8b2ec8ecd12defdc1dfd1cc27e4358866 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Marcus <marcusvds83@gmail.com>
Date: Mon, 15 Jun 2026 16:36:22 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] fix: aceitar cancelamento via API iFood para homologacao

- Adicionado accept_cancellation() e reject_cancellation() no IFoodAPIClient
- Webhook CAN/CANCELLATION_REQUESTED agora envia confirmacao ao iFood
- Evento CAR tratado separadamente
- Logs detalhados com prefixo [CANCELLATION] para rastreabilidade
- Rotas manuais /accept-cancellation e /reject-cancellation para testes

Cenario Pedido Cancelado reprovado (0/10) na homologacao anterior.
Causa: middleware so atualizava Odoo sem responder ao iFood.
---
 app/routes/ifood_webhooks.py | 44 +++++++++++++++++++++---
 app/routes/orders.py         | 66 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 app/services/ifood_api.py    | 49 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 3 files changed, 154 insertions(+), 5 deletions(-)

diff --git a/app/routes/ifood_webhooks.py b/app/routes/ifood_webhooks.py
